text: Police Nurse is a 1963 American crime drama movie directed by Maury Dexter and starring Ken Scott, Merry Anders, Oscar Beregi (Jr.), Byron Morrow, Ivan Bonar, Carol Brewster. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * Category:1963 crime movies Category:1963 drama movies Category:1960s American crime drama movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by Maury Dexter
